Dynamic query with TanStack Query caching.

```typescript
const balance = await reactor.fetchQueryDynamic({
  functionName: "icrc1_balance_of",
  candid: "(record { owner : principal }) -> (nat) query",
  args: [{ owner: "aaaaa-aa" }],
})
// Subsequent calls return cached result
```

